  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Women faith leaders as peacebuilders and advocates against gender-based violence</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Increased women&#x2019;s meaningful and representative participation in peacebuilding fora at community and national levels.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The following activities will be implemented;
- National conference on women&#x2019;s inclusion in the peace process organised
- Establish an interactive peacebuilding link and GBV focused platform at national level for women policy-makers, parliamentarians and faith leaders
- Mapping of peace/dialogue fora at community, county and state levels, and link to the established national platform/s
- Capacity building of 250 women in leadership, GBV and peacebuilding at county and state levels through training and mentorship</narrative>
  </description>
